Certainly! Below is an example of a website layout focusing on Travis Scott:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Travis Scott Fan Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    header {
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav {
      background-color: #333;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
    main {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: black;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Travis Scott Fan Page</h1>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Biography</a>
    <a href="#">Discography</a>
    <a href="#">Tour Dates</a>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <h2>Welcome to the Travis Scott Fan Page</h2>
    <p>Here you will find information about Travis Scott, his music, and upcoming events.</p>

    <h3>Biography</h3>
    <p>Travis Scott is an American rapper, singer, and songwriter. He gained fame for his critically acclaimed albums and energetic performances.</p>

    <h3>Discography</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Album 1</li>
      <li>Album 2</li>
      <li>Album 3</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Tour Dates</h3>
    <p>Check out the upcoming tour dates to catch Travis Scott live in concert.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Date 1 - City</li>
      <li>Date 2 - City</li>
      <li>Date 3 - City</li>
    </ul>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2021 Travis Scott Fan Page</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

In this example, the HTML code structure includes a header with the page title, a navigation bar, a main content section with information about Travis Scott, and a footer. The CSS styles within the `head` section define the appearance of various elements on the webpage.

Please note that this is a basic example, and you can customize the content and style to match your preferences and add more information about Travis Scott, such as photos, videos, interviews, or any other relevant details.
